data.description: Fabulous brick ranch, great curb appeal and easy to maintain xeriscape front yard.  Close to Village East Park & Elementary school! There's nothing like this at this price that features a new roof, new interior paint, large sunroom (not included in the square footage) and incredible location. Enter into the formal living room, or bonus room. The family room has a cozy fireplace and open to the  fully equipped kitchen includes the stove, dishwasher, refrigerator and microwave. A convenient main floor laundry has easy access to all three bedrooms. The bathrooms have been remodeled, and the basement bathroom features a large custom steam shower.  The spacious basement is an open canvas to do with as you want or fabulous storage.  The three season sunroom overlooks the shady backyard, and a dog run is great for any canine family members as well. The roof is only one year old, and has recently been inspected. This home is only steps to Village East Park as well as Village East Elementary School. Located in the award winning Cherry Creek school district, all three levels of schools are within easy walking distance. Easy access to Utah Park & Pool, DTC, Fitzsimons Medical Campus, Buckley SFB, DIA and downtown.
